****************************************
        Compiling/Execution
****************************************
1) type 'make goodcnt' to compile question 2 answer/modified program igoodcnt.c
2) type 'make badcnt' to compile question 1 given file ibadcnt.c
3) type './igoodcnt 2000' to execute question 2 executible with NITER of 2000
    - error checking includes number of arguments, valid integer for NITER
4) type './ibadcnt' to execute question 1 program
